title: How to log in to the Web Management Page of B593s-931
answer:
Follow these steps to log in to the web management page: 

 1. Connect CPE cables. 

 2. Configure the computer's IP address so that the IP addresses of the computer and the device are in the same network segment. 

 3. Open the browser, and enter [http://192.168.1.1](http://192.168.1.1/) in the address box. 

 4. Enter the user name and password to log in to the web management page. 

 **Note:** 

 The default user name is **admin**, and the default password is **admin**.
